name: In Smoke He Rises
description:
This is Sean Derrick Cooper Marquardt, an amazing musician and artist living in Berlin.  He has some of the most beautiful, piercing eyes I have ever seen.  He was amazingly generous to let me shoot him in a smoke filled room, wandering among the ropes, adorned in fur.  

Model is @seanderrickcoopermarquardt
Photo and wardrobe Bubbles And Frown

All vegan materials
